Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:29.01,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沸腾热血摇撼世间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:35.81,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无明忿怒噬尽生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:42.10,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将泪水与悲叹 尽皆忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:48.70,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便在战斗中 不支倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.86,0:01:51.90,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的灵魂一兆度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:55.21,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他的灵魂一兆度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:58.37,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从无底深渊中复活再起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.06,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤红之心是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:02.39,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火 烈火 烈火 烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.62,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不灭！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:07.80,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.96,0:02:11.02,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的污秽尽皆除去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:14.43,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.51,0:02:17.82,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将它的心脏煮熟烧透
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.98,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:24.17,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将你的能量燃烧殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:27.28,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧 燃吧燃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.32,Opening,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的目光疯狂如炬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:36.62,Opening,,0000,0000,0000,,翻译:zsirius  时间轴：yuki king 后期:投影

Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼~噜~ 呼~噜~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河水变成温泉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.44,0:02:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有陨石砸下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.29,0:03:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.87,0:03:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎天狗

